file.name: ExecuteResponse.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
ExecuteResponse:
  type: object
  description: The object that contains responses from execute `pageLoad` and/or execute regional `mboxes` request.
  properties:
    pageLoad:
      $ref: "./PageLoadResponse.yaml#/PageLoadResponse"
    mboxes:
      type: array
      description: The list of responses for requested regional mboxes.
      items:
        $ref: "./MboxResponse.yaml#/MboxResponse"
